2.22. Changes to these card terms and conditions
:SKRSLUT.
.br
These card terms and conditions can be altered with immediate effect
if the changes in question are to your benefit. Otherwise, the card
terms and conditions and price list can only be altered on two
months' notice. You will be notified of any such changes in writing
or electronically. You are obliged to notify &BANKNAVN. of any
changes in your address or email address. Any failure to do so that
results in you not being notified of changes will be your responsibility.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
In the event of changes to the regulations, these will be considered
accepted unless you inform &BANKNAVN. that you do not wish to be bound by
the new regulations, prior to the date on which they come into effect.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
